headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
Those looking to customize and move exotic vehicles can pick up an Auto Shop (and all its Renovations, Modifications, and Upgrades) for 30% off this week.

Players who own a Celebrity Solutions Agency can pick up the Coil Compact EMP Launcher for 25% off this week from the Agency Armory.
